latestIgtvVideos.title: 💗💗💗💗💗LETS WINGED IT WITH BOLD LIPS... 💕💕💕💕💕
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
With the limited products we can create different types of looks, all just depends on your creativity.
So in this tutorial-
I didnt play the layering game, I have just used the foundation @lorealpro (truematch)and for fixing it @maybelline (fitme compact).
A single product can play so many roles . 
On my eyes i have used the highlighter and bronzer as well on the parts where it is meant to be used.
THATS IT.💞
